":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":32457,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/06\/24\/islam-imaan-yaqeen\/","url_meta":{"origin":359,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Faith: The Prophet explains Islam, Iman, and Yaqin","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"June 24, 2019","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Firas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAsk me about whatever you wish.\u201d A man called out, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what is Islam?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cTo perform prayer and give charity.\u201d The man said, \u201cWhat is faith?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cSincerity.\u201d\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":17315,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/12\/26\/neglect-part-islam\/","url_meta":{"origin":359,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Islam: Whoever neglects these has abandoned part of Islam","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 26, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cIslam is to worship Allah without associating any partner with Him, to establish prayer, to give charity, to fast the month of Ramadan, to perform pilgrimage to the House, to enjoin good and forbid evil, and to greet\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u06